### Uninstall a runtime (drains active leases first)
DELETE http://localhost:7878/api/v1/backends/ri_9f3a1c2e HTTP/1.1

### Response 204 — no active leases
HTTP/1.1 204 No Content

### Response 409 — active leases require confirmation
HTTP/1.1 409 Conflict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "RUNTIME_IN_USE",
    "category": "conflict",
    "message": "ri_9f3a1c2e has 2 active leases; retry with ?force=true to drain them first",
    "dependents": [
      {"extension_id": "local-llm", "lease_ids": ["rl_7c4b2d10", "rl_3a891f44"]}
    ]
  }
}

### Force uninstall with drain
DELETE http://localhost:7878/api/v1/backends/ri_9f3a1c2e?force=true HTTP/1.1

### Response 204 — leases drained, runtime removed
HTTP/1.1 204 No Content
